Description_lang: Brann leaps into battle with concussive force, dealing damage and taunting enemies nearby.

description_blz.en_US: Brann leaps into battle with concussive force, dealing damage and taunting enemies nearby.
description_blz.es_MX: Brann salta a la batalla con una fuerza conmocionante, lo que inflige daño y provoca a los enemigos cercanos.
description_blz.pt_BR: Brann salta em batalha com força concussiva, causando dano e provocando os inimigos próximos.
description_blz.de_DE: Brann springt mit erschütternder Kraft in den Kampf, fügt Gegnern in der Nähe Schaden zu und verspottet sie.
description_blz.en_GB: Brann leaps into battle with concussive force, dealing damage and taunting enemies nearby.
description_blz.es_ES: Brann entra en combate con una fuerza conmocionadora que inflige daño y provoca a los enemigos cercanos.
description_blz.fr_FR: Brann bondit dans la bataille avec une force considérable, infligeant des dégâts et provoquant les personnages adverses proches.
description_blz.it_IT: Brann salta in battaglia con forza concussiva, infliggendo danni e provocando i nemici vicini.

description_blz.ko_KR: 브란이 충격파를 일으키며 전투에 돌입해, 주위의 적에게 피해를 입히고 도발합니다.
description_blz.zh_TW: 布萊恩以震撼性的力量加入戰局，造成傷害，並嘲諷附近敵人。
description_blz.zh_CN: 布莱恩以强大的冲击力跃入战斗，造成伤害并嘲讽周围的敌人。
